parameters.name: CertName
parameters.description: The name of the SM certificate.

parameters.name: EncryptCertificate
parameters.description: The content of the SM certificate.

parameters.name: EncryptPrivateKey
parameters.description: The private key of the SM certificate.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description:
The ID of the WAF instance.

>  You can call the [DescribeInstance](~~433756~~) operation to query the ID of the WAF instance.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The region in which the WAF instance is deployed. Valid values:

*   **cn-hangzhou**: Chinese mainland.
*   **ap-southeast-1**: outside the Chinese mainland.

parameters.name: ResourceManagerResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the Alibaba Cloud resource group.

parameters.name: SignCertificate
parameters.description: The content of the signing certificate for the SM certificate.

parameters.name: SignPrivateKey
parameters.description: The private key of the signing certificate for the SM certificate.
